Description: # jinjarg
        
        CLI-template renderer like m4 but based on jinja2 and argparse.
        
        ## Installation
        
        ``` shell
        pip install jinjarg
        ```
        
        ## Usage example
        
        Take a look at [example](/example) directory.
        
        ## Why
        
        There is jinja-cli and it's fine... until you need logic that doesn't fit in Jinja.
        
